raw_text = "~ start
PlayerM: Mom! You're still online?
PlayerM: You're up way later than usual
PlayerM: Mom? You there?
Mom: Ah hi baby, just give me a second
PlayerM: Did you see my latest post?
Mom: One second baby
Mom: Which one honey? 😊
PlayerM: The one from today!
PlayerM: Actually wait
PlayerM: That weird guy didn't comment this time 🤔
PlayerM: Huh
Mom: Oh really? That's good then right? 😊
PlayerM: Yeah but... I'm sorry you had to see it. It was just a club thing
PlayerM: So embarrassing 🙈
PlayerM: Wait actually, you didn't comment either mom
PlayerM: Did you see it? 🤔
Mom: Oh! I'm sorry sweetie I didn't, I was so busy today!
Mom: I didn't get a chance to look at it yet 😞
PlayerM: Hmm
PlayerM: You said last time he wouldn't be commenting anymore
PlayerM: How did you know that? 🤔
Mom: I just had a feeling! You know how these internet people are
Mom: They come and go 😅
PlayerM: I guess...
PlayerM: Anyway!
PlayerM: What were you doing?
Mom: Oh just you know.. chatting with a friend
PlayerM: Chatting with a friend? This late? 😆
PlayerM: Ive never seen you chat on your phone for over a minute unless it's with me
Mom: You know how it is, household is a bit lonely with you gone so moms gotta socialize a little 🥰
PlayerM: Well as long as you're happy! 😊
Mom: Mom is happier and healthier than ever 😌 Look
Mom: img: mom/7
Mom: Your mom's doing fine
PlayerM: Is it hot or something? You're sweating a little
Mom: Ah right, I'll turn on the AC in a bit
PlayerM: Yeah make sure you take care of yourself mom, I don't want you getting sick omg
Mom: Don't worry baby 😘
PlayerM: You owe me the rest of that story by the way 😁
PlayerM: You can't just leave me hanging
Mom: Haha okay okay
Mom: Where did I leave off? 
PlayerM: You were telling me about your boyfriend
PlayerM: The one before dad
PlayerM: You never told me his name by the way! 😤
Mom: Oh! His name was Theodore
Mom: But I always called him Theo ☺️
PlayerM: Theo 🥺
PlayerM: That's such a cute name
Mom: He was a cute boy hehe
Mom: He went to the music school on campus actually
PlayerM: He was a musician?? 😍
Mom: Mhmm! He played the violin
Mom: He was really talented too
Mom: I used to sit and listen to him practice for hours
Mom: I'd just curl up nearby with a book and let him play
PlayerM: That sounds like a dream 🥹
Mom: It was
Mom: He actually wrote me a piece once
Mom: Just for me
PlayerM: HE WROTE YOU A SONG??
PlayerM: That's the most romantic thing I've ever heard 😭
Mom: It really was
Mom: When he played it for the first time I cried
Mom: Mom's tough but there are 3 times in my life I seriously cried and that was one of them
PlayerM: Oh really?? I cry like every other night LOL
PlayerM: What were the other two?
Mom: Well, one is the day you were born 🥰
PlayerM: Awwh really?
Mom: Mhmm, I was so happy that I had you I was just so overwhelmed!
Mom: You were crying with me too 😊
PlayerM: I was a baby 😆
Mom: You still are my baby 😘
Mom: Now where was I?
PlayerM: He wrote you a song
Mom: It was sooo beautiful and delicate, just like he was 😊
Mom: He also had a big performance in the national theater hall
Mom: img: mom/8
Mom: I had front seat tickets as a special guest
PlayerM: Omg that's so fancy! And you look really pretty!
Mom: Thanks honey
Mom: I was so proud of him
PlayerM: So you're describing the most dreamy guy ever 😂
PlayerM: But I don't understand
PlayerM: Why did you break up with him??
PlayerM: How does dad fit into all of this? 🤔
PlayerM: You said they didn't get along
Mom: Slow down honey 😚
PlayerM: Eep sowwy
Mom: So your dad was kind of the opposite of Theo
Mom: He was loud and confident and still everyone on campus knew who he was and respected him
Mom: All the girls thought he was hot and all that
PlayerM: Did you? 😶
Mom: It was a bit complicated
Mom: At the time I thought how could anyone like this total muscle head sleazebag
Mom: So no, I didn't like him at all actually 😄
Mom: But wrestling team was a pretty big deal at our school
PlayerM: Did he pick on Theo?
Mom: Well... yeah 😅
Mom: One day Theo was walking back from practice carrying his violin case
Mom: And your dad was sitting with his little college gang when we passed by
Mom: He had like four or five guys behind him and two girls hanging off his arms 🙄
Mom: Like something out of a movie
PlayerM: Oh seriously? Dad was like that? 🤯
Mom: 100%
Mom: They started laughing in Theo's direction
Mom: And poor Theo thought they were laughing at him
Mom: He decided for some reason to stand up against them 🥺
PlayerM: Omg
Mom: It was against his nature but honestly, I realized that it was the hottest thing I had ever seen Theo do
PlayerM: Wow really?
Mom: Mhmm! My heart was beating so fast so I let him do his thing
PlayerM: Well.. how did it go?
Mom: Wellll, he tried his best 😅 They ended up pushing him down
Mom: It was a very short lived experience
PlayerM: Poor Theo
Mom: Mhmm, I had to step in and yell at them
Mom: Your dad took two steps back the moment he saw me 😆
Mom: I'm not sure I should have done that
PlayerM: Why not? Weren't you protecting Theo?
Mom: Yeah but I felt like it got worse after I stepped in
Mom: I got right in your dad's face and told him he was nothing but a bully
Mom: That picking on someone half his size didn't make him tough, it made him pathetic
PlayerM: MOM srsly? 😳
PlayerM: You said that to his face??
Mom: I was super mad 😡🤭
Mom: I think I even took a picture of it
Mom: img: mom/9
PlayerM: Omg I've never seen you that mad 😱 SCARY
Mom: His friends went all quiet
Mom: Even those girls on his arms didn't know what to do
Mom: And your dad just looked at me
Mom: Even I was a bit confused cause he went totally quiet 😅
PlayerM: Then what happened??
Mom: I grabbed Theo's hand and pulled him up and walked away
Mom: I was fuming the whole walk back
PlayerM: Good! Dad totally deserved that!
PlayerM: ...
PlayerM: 🤔
PlayerM: WHY IS HE MY DAD THEN??
Mom: 😂
Mom: It's seriously getting super late honey, you should go to bed
Mom: We can talk about it more later!
PlayerM: Mooom I don't want any cliff hangers 😩
Mom: I promise I'll tell you everything
Mom: But you have class tomorrow so get some sleep 😠
PlayerM: Eep! Yes ma'am 🫡
Mom: Good girl
PlayerM: But you PROMISE you'll tell me the rest?
Mom: Of course I promise sweetheart 🩷
Mom: Love you 😘
PlayerM: Love you too mom 😤🩷 Good night
=> END
"
